==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Transmogrification
<hw>Trans*mog`ri*fi*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The
act of transmogrifying, or the state of being transmogrified;
transformation.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Clive, who wrote me about the <qex>transmogrification</qex> of our
schoolfellow, an attorney's son.</q> <rj><qau>Thackeray.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Transmogrify</ent>⟦br⟧
